short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Build an Extension to get the rate-my-professor score when selecting courses!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find annoying to search every professor's rate when registering UW-Madison's courses? UW-Madison-Professor-Hunter helps to you do that more efficiently! Just click "RATE IT" on the popup page when viewing professors on MyUW's course search and enroll. The rate-my-professor scores will be automatically attached to the page.
